Class EventTextSet

All Implemented Interfaces:
HasAttributes
public final class EventTextSet
extends HltContent
implements HasAttributes

Represents a set of event occurrence. This can be used, for example, to represent event coreference which doesn't bother about arguments. THe types of the contained events are allowed to be heterogeneous.

For high-level documentation of all event classes, see DocumentEvent.

This class is locally immutable.
